{
  "texts": [
    "AI systems can perpetuate racial, gender, cultural, and age-related biases present in their training data ((Gross, 2023; Gupta et al., 2025).",
    "Even annotator bias can influence model behavior (Liu, 2022).",
    "Moreover, models are eager to justify their incorrect outputs (Ji et al., 2023; Mollick, 2024).",
    "Recall that models have no morality (Olson, 2024).",
    "This issue demands rigorous review and in-built correction mechanisms within clinical contexts."
  ]
}